---
title: Easy Seared Garlic Butter Steak with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: We’ve dug deep to find and create this stunning meal for tonight’s dinner. A roast root veggie toss, with pops of colour from the beetroot, adds an earthen texture to the succulent beef rump, slathered in a buttery garlic sauce. We know you will be excavating this plate down to the last crumb.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
